{"tid":917074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支持本地拳手？得曹星如一個？","createTime":"2018-11-26T06:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T09:03:05.000Z","uid":93036,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3a5289555e2cbc009089606425672f98415cda","tid":917074,"uid":93036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"一個年度本地冠軍賽張poster 可以一場爭腰帶既拳手都冇？<br />\n主辦單位有冇尊重過一班打左成年績分賽既拳手？<br />\n你大頭放名星無問題，但其他努力左一年既拳手呢？係咪唔紅就唔洗尊重？<br />\nPoster 又冇份，媒體又唔報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/143705_26881d121bd51da8fefc1fd1f8b0cfdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F143705_26881d121bd51da8fefc1fd1f8b0cfdb.jpg&h=9f63890a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n錯既不在曹星如，佢拿自己出黎promote 呢場比賽，但主辦單位就咁放晒焦點係曹星如道，其他本地選手就隻字不提，咁樣係支持一項運動咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：只係一位拳迷，唔係拳手<br />\n支持曹星如亦支持其他運動員"},{"pid":"05812b4c71fa1fc9580c16ef056c37a12d5b1f07","tid":917074,"uid":93036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010432f8a38e52b45b714e86aee7958a9f27399b","tid":917074,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"話說其中一個拳手，仲要係琴日用手機影下硬照交比拳總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該無人知叫咩名"},{"pid":"eb8c1838af00ecf2b81abc738e2b16bd94e21454","tid":917074,"uid":93036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"010432f8a38e52b45b714e86aee7958a9f27399b","tid":917074,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"話說其中一個拳手，仲要係琴日用手機影下硬照交比拳總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該無人知叫咩名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"真係好鄧佢地唔抵，辛苦打左成年，連張相都冇"},{"pid":"857841767fa81262a42d2229937267899cfe5bdf","tid":917074,"uid":93036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit